Hi Rafaella,
Please find my response to your enquiries in the body of the email below in=
 blue.
Attachments and emails also provided for reference. Any concerns you have p=
lease do not hesitate to ask me =E2=80=93 as always I remain ready to meet =
with you at your property to have further discussions or revisions.
Best Regards,
Grant.

